message.entry: First input must be a java object
Callback name unrecognized for {0}. \nValid callbacks are:\n {1}
JAVACOMPONENT is not supported on this platform

WARNING: This feature is not supported in MATLAB and the API and 
functionality may change in a future release. 

usage: javacomponent(javaClassName, position, parent, callback) 
- position can be empty, [left bottom width height] in pixels 
 or the character vector North, South, East, or West.
- parent can be a figure or a uitoolbar handle.
- callback can be empty or a cell array of JavaEvents and their handlers.
